<!--
    Marathi (मराठी) — mr
    Script : Devanagari; LTR.  Rendered via Noto Sans Devanagari (bundled API 21+).
    Approx.: ~95 M L1 speakers (Maharashtra, Goa, India; diaspora).
    Register: Standard Modern Marathi (प्रमाण मराठी) as used in print media
              and official communication.
    Notes  : Marathi uses the same Devanagari script as Hindi but has distinct
             vocabulary, grammar, and honorifics.  Masculine/feminine grammatical
             gender is pervasive.  "Binge drinking" → अतिमद्यपान.
    Source : Translated from values-de/strings.xml (German source of truth).
-->
